469
00:49:29,640 --> 00:49:31,153
Lopta u sredini.

470
00:49:33,720 --> 00:49:35,392
Hajde, inspektore.

471
00:49:41,040 --> 00:49:42,837
Hajde ...

472
00:49:44,880 --> 00:49:46,598
Kakav veliki udarac.

473
00:49:46,800 --> 00:49:49,109
Mogli ste da igrate
u reprezentaciji.

474
00:49:49,320 --> 00:49:53,791
Dečaci, inspektor
je dobar igrač.

475
00:49:56,440 --> 00:49:59,671
Svi mi ovde smo dobri ljudi.
Imajte to na umu.

476
00:50:08,840 --> 00:50:11,593
Znači Vi tvrdite

477
00:50:11,840 --> 00:50:14,718
da ste prisutnog Korado Katanija

478
00:50:14,920 --> 00:50:18,799
pomenutog dana videli,

479
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:21,673
kako ulazi u kuću g. Ravanusa

480
00:50:21,960 --> 00:50:25,714
Nakon što ste prethodno video
navedenog g Ravanusa

481
00:50:25,920 --> 00:50:28,480
