582
01:00:13,480 --> 01:00:15,471
I Paoline takođe.

583
01:00:17,720 --> 01:00:20,154
Mislim da sam uzeo sve.

584
01:00:23,520 --> 01:00:26,353
Mnogo sam razmišljala.

585
01:00:28,400 --> 01:00:30,630
Možda sam želela muža

586
01:00:30,840 --> 01:00:33,149
